e prefix \"St.\", as in \"Saint\", is alphabetized as if it were spelled out.\n\n==[[NCAA]]==\n\n===[[NCAA Division I|Division I]]===\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n! rowspan=3|Team !! rowspan=3|School !! rowspan=3|City !! rowspan=3|Conference !! colspan=7|Sport sponsorship\n|-\n! rowspan=2|Foot-<br/>ball !! colspan=2|Basketball !! rowspan=2|Base-<br/>ball !! rowspan=2|Soft-<br/>ball !! colspan=2|Soccer\n|-\n! M !! W !! M !! W\n|-\n| [[Bethune\u2013Cookman Wildcats]] || [[Bethune\u2013Cookman University]] || [[Daytona Beach, Florida|Daytona Beach]] || [[Mid-Eastern Athletic Conference|MEAC]] || style=\"background:#D2FFD2; text-align:center\"|[[NCAA Division I Football Championship Subdivision|FCS]] || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{na}} || {{na}}\n|-\n| [[FIU Panthers]] || [[Florida International University]] || [[Miami]] || [[Conference USA|C-USA]] || style=\"background:#D2FFD2; text-align:center\"|[[NCAA Division I Football Bowl Subdivision|FBS]] || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}}\n|-\n| [[Florida Gators]] || [[University of Florida]] || [[Gainesville, Florida|Gainesville]] || [[Southeastern Conference|SEC]] || style=\"background:#D2FFD2; text-align:center\"|[[NCAA Division I Football Bowl Subdivision|FBS]] || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{na}} || {{ya}}\n|-\n| [[Florida A&M Rattlers|Florida A&M Rattlers and Lady Rattlers]] || [[Florida A&M University]] || [[Tallahassee, Florida|Tallahassee]] || [[Mid-Eastern Athletic Conference|MEAC]] || style=\"background:#D2FFD2; text-align:center\"|[[NCAA Division I Football Championship Subdivision|FCS]] || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{na}} || {{na}}\n|-\n| [[Florida Atlantic Owls]] || [[Florida Atlantic University]] || [[Boca Raton, Florida|Boca Raton]] || [[Conference USA|C-USA]] || style=\"background:#D2FFD2; text-align:center\"|[[NCAA Division I Football Bowl Subdivision|FBS]] || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}}\n|-\n| [[Florida Gulf Coast Eagles]] || [[Florida Gulf Coast University]] || [[Fort Myers, Florida|Fort Myers]] || [[Atlantic Sun Conference|Atlantic Sun]] || {{na}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}}\n|-\n| [[Florida State Seminoles]] || [[Florida State University]] || [[Tallahassee, Florida|Tallahassee]] || [[Atlantic Coast Conference|ACC]] || style=\"background:#D2FFD2; text-align:center\"|[[NCAA Division I Football Bowl Subdivision|FBS]] || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{na}} || {{ya}}\n|-\n| [[Jacksonville Dolphins]] || [[Jacksonville University]] || [[Jacksonville, Florida|Jacksonville]] || [[Atlantic Sun Conference|Atlantic Sun]] || style=\"background:#D2FFD2; text-align:center\"|[[NCAA Division I Football Championship Subdivision|FCS]] {{efn|Jacksonville's football team, which competes in the [[Pioneer Football League]], will be discontinued in 2020\u201321.}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}}\n|-\n| [[Miami Hurricanes]] || [[University of Miami]] || [[Coral Gables, Florida|Coral Gables]] || [[Atlantic Coast Conference|ACC]] || style=\"background:#D2FFD2; text-align:center\"|[[NCAA Division I Football Bowl Subdivision|FBS]] || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{na}} || {{na}} || {{ya}}\n|-\n| [[North Florida Ospreys]] || [[University of North Florida]] || [[Jacksonville, Florida|Jacksonville]] || [[Atlantic Sun Conference|Atlantic Sun]] || {{na}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}}\n|-\n| [[South Florida Bulls]] || [[University of South Florida]] || [[Tampa, Florida|Tampa]] || {{sort|American|[[American Athletic Conference|The American]]}} || style=\"background:#D2FFD2; text-align:center\"|[[NCAA Division I Football Bowl Subdivision|FBS]] || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}} || {{ya}}\n|-\n| [[Stetson Hatters]] || [[Stetson University]] || [[DeLand, Florida|DeLand]] || [[Atlantic Sun Conference|Atlantic Sun]] || style=\"background:#D2FFD2; text-align:center\"|[[NCAA Division I Football 